WEBVTT

01:38.160 --> 01:40.560
EPISODE 6

01:44.680 --> 01:46.760
So many servers?

01:47.400 --> 01:50.080
Can pigs fly now?

01:50.160 --> 01:51.680
You're getting into gaming?

01:52.120 --> 01:53.600
I have to try it one by one.

01:53.920 --> 01:55.080
Searching for servers is tiring.

01:55.160 --> 01:56.920
Here, have a drink.

01:57.000 --> 01:58.360
- Thanks!
- Thanks.

02:00.640 --> 02:04.120
Could it be that
Bei Weiwei is playing this game,

02:04.360 --> 02:06.320
but you don't know which server she's on?

02:06.520 --> 02:09.759
Yeah, but I know her handle.

02:10.479 --> 02:12.240
Bro, you're amazing.

02:12.360 --> 02:13.720
Have fun looking.

02:19.240 --> 02:20.760
Which one is it?

03:16.160 --> 03:18.080
This is when we agreed
to release the video.

03:19.440 --> 03:20.440
It's been uploaded!

03:44.880 --> 03:48.680
GIRL BANDIT ABDUCTS GROOM

04:03.640 --> 04:05.600
Oh, no! Bandits!

04:05.840 --> 04:07.560
What do you want, Girl Bandit?

04:08.000 --> 04:10.600
I own this mountain.
I planted these trees.

04:10.680 --> 04:12.400
For a safe passage through,
leave the man as tribute.

04:12.480 --> 04:13.760
No can do!

04:50.920 --> 04:55.200
You detest me so. Leave here.
I set you free.

06:30.760 --> 06:32.120
You have such a bright future.

06:32.200 --> 06:34.840
Why must you waste away
on this desolate mountain?

07:02.640 --> 07:03.960
How did this happen?

07:04.280 --> 07:05.360
When we shot the ending,

07:05.440 --> 07:07.560
Girl Bandit dies,

07:07.640 --> 07:09.280
and Guzheng Player jumps off
the Sunset Peak

07:09.360 --> 07:11.240
with her body in his arms.

07:12.120 --> 07:14.280
I can't believe Naihe made
such a melodramatic change to the ending.

07:14.960 --> 07:18.480
If people find out
that I cried watching the video...

07:18.640 --> 07:20.280
Would it be embarrassing?

07:29.600 --> 07:31.760
I watched it. It's very good.

07:56.600 --> 07:58.320
Did you change the ending?

08:06.480 --> 08:09.640
Yes, otherwise
the running time is too short.

08:19.600 --> 08:22.080
Running time? What running time?

08:22.160 --> 08:24.520
I remember the video can be any length.

08:26.400 --> 08:27.640
In the detailed guidelines,

08:27.720 --> 08:29.640
the winning video
that is over 30 minutes long

08:29.720 --> 08:32.039
will receive double the reward.

08:32.720 --> 08:35.640
We already took the time to make it.
We should earn all we can.

08:39.200 --> 08:41.159
That's what makes him the master player.

08:41.360 --> 08:43.440
He's even studied the detailed guidelines.

08:43.559 --> 08:45.960
But, are you that confident

08:46.040 --> 08:47.560
we will win for sure?

08:47.720 --> 08:49.920
No. That's not the point.

08:50.240 --> 08:51.600
The point is,

08:51.800 --> 08:53.480
according to Naihe,

08:53.680 --> 08:57.240
the ending plot
that nearly drove me to tears

08:57.360 --> 08:59.880
was added to stretch the running time?

09:03.840 --> 09:08.320
How did you come up with the ending?

09:08.400 --> 09:11.000
It's much better than the original one.

09:12.600 --> 09:13.920
The original ending was good,

09:14.480 --> 09:16.680
but it wouldn't work well with flashbacks.

09:17.640 --> 09:18.800
It'd be too obvious.

09:23.480 --> 09:25.360
So, the ending was changed,

09:25.560 --> 09:28.080
to fit in flashbacks
and stretch the running time?

09:32.880 --> 09:33.760
More or less.

09:37.280 --> 09:39.720
I see. Naihe wanted
to stretch the running time.

09:39.800 --> 09:42.920
Not only that, he also inserted
a bunch of flashbacks.

09:43.200 --> 09:46.320
The new ending is a product of
stretching for time and laziness.

09:46.680 --> 09:47.920
All that heart-wrenching,

09:48.000 --> 09:50.000
longing after separation by death

09:50.120 --> 09:52.040
is just a lot of nothing.

09:53.480 --> 09:56.720
I was too naive to be so moved by it.

09:59.680 --> 10:01.880
Let's publish it to the forum.

10:02.240 --> 10:03.880
Will you do it? Or me?

10:04.120 --> 10:06.640
You do it. I'm too lazy to register.

10:14.360 --> 10:15.920
Okay. I'll get on it.

10:39.400 --> 10:41.800
The comments are pouring in,
right after I posted.

10:41.880 --> 10:44.800
Have you read them? Many people cried.

10:44.880 --> 10:46.560
The beginning and the end
are so melodramatic.

10:46.640 --> 10:48.440
They're all slamming the script writer.

10:48.720 --> 10:50.200
I took the blame for you.

10:50.520 --> 10:52.400
You put down my name as the script writer.

10:57.160 --> 11:00.800
I haven't read them.
Let me know the result.

11:08.880 --> 11:12.600
Okay. I'll report back to you every day.

11:17.520 --> 11:20.640
Why does Guzheng Player
have to kill Girl Bandit?

11:25.360 --> 11:28.440
I'm pretty sure you wrote that part.

11:33.600 --> 11:35.320
But I was playing around.

11:35.800 --> 11:39.360
If it were you,
would you kill Girl Bandit?

11:45.120 --> 11:46.040
Not me.

11:49.960 --> 11:50.800
Hmm?

11:54.960 --> 11:57.520
He's not me. I wouldn't reach that point.

12:07.200 --> 12:09.960
I should go.
There's not a soul in the library.

12:14.360 --> 12:15.400
I'm sure there are.

12:20.680 --> 12:22.840
It's true! How did you know?

12:24.720 --> 12:27.320
Lucky guess. Be safe on the way back.

12:30.480 --> 12:31.320
Okay.

12:48.120 --> 12:50.680
- Thanks, Professor. Bye-bye.
- Okay. Bye-bye.

13:42.520 --> 13:44.400
Why are you still in Pujia Village?

13:44.680 --> 13:46.520
Didn't I bump you up to grade 30?

13:47.880 --> 13:50.640
I have the highest grade in Pujia Village.

13:50.960 --> 13:53.320
That's why I'm reluctant to leave.

13:53.600 --> 13:55.960
The outside world is full of danger.

13:56.040 --> 13:59.200
Look at this place.
It's greenery everywhere and I reign big.

13:59.520 --> 14:01.680
I'm surrounded by silly newbies.

14:02.680 --> 14:05.680
I have to soak in the feeling of being
the best and most famous.

14:06.600 --> 14:08.600
Real masters like you

14:08.680 --> 14:11.520
can't relate to a fake master like me.

14:15.440 --> 14:16.360
You startled me.

14:16.520 --> 14:18.640
Enough. Go do your thing.

14:18.800 --> 14:20.840
I just discovered the fun of gaming.

14:20.920 --> 14:22.120
I don't need your help for now.

14:24.120 --> 14:25.000
I'll go wash my face.

15:14.520 --> 15:18.640
Help.

15:33.120 --> 15:36.040
Help me, Weiwei!

15:37.760 --> 15:39.640
Help me out, Weiwei!

15:40.000 --> 15:40.960
What is it?

15:41.040 --> 15:44.680
This can wait.
It's life and death over here!

15:44.760 --> 15:47.920
What can be so urgent in Pujia Village?

15:48.120 --> 15:49.960
You have a high grade.
Who'd challenge you?

15:50.480 --> 15:51.680
Not me!

15:51.760 --> 15:54.080
I saw someone in trouble,
so I went to his rescue,

15:56.480 --> 16:00.280
but I ran into
a particularly nimble monster.

16:00.560 --> 16:02.000
My maneuvering can't keep up.

16:04.000 --> 16:05.240
Come on.

16:08.320 --> 16:10.480
Have a seat, Ms. Weiwei.

16:11.280 --> 16:14.400
Drink this and show them
who's the real boss.

16:20.760 --> 16:22.160
Okay.

16:46.840 --> 16:49.520
- Done. It's all yours.
- Thank you so much!

16:49.720 --> 16:51.680
- I want milk tomorrow.
- No problem.

17:00.840 --> 17:01.960
Please wait!

17:05.240 --> 17:06.920
Thanks for coming to my rescue.

17:09.599 --> 17:10.480
In this world,

17:10.560 --> 17:12.599
ability comes with responsibility.

17:12.680 --> 17:15.359
That was my duty. See you later.

17:15.520 --> 17:16.400
Wait!

17:17.680 --> 17:18.520
Are you talking to me?

17:19.599 --> 17:21.839
This is my first experience with gaming.

17:21.920 --> 17:23.079
You saw it yourself.

17:23.160 --> 17:25.520
I was powerless
against the weakest monster.

17:25.599 --> 17:27.800
You're amazing!
Won't you take me under your wing?

17:29.960 --> 17:32.280
This dummy says I'm amazing.

17:32.440 --> 17:33.480
With him by my side,

17:33.560 --> 17:35.680
it'll be nice to get praised all the time.

17:35.760 --> 17:39.680
It's rare to find someone
who's worse off than me when I started.

17:41.840 --> 17:44.080
Fine, I'll take you under my wing,

17:44.160 --> 17:45.280
until you can fight monsters on your own.

17:47.520 --> 17:49.320
Master, accept my honoring bow
as your apprentice.

17:50.360 --> 17:52.320
Did I say I'd take him as my apprentice?

17:52.400 --> 17:56.480
I got an apprentice
before leaving Pujia Village! What a deal!

17:57.880 --> 18:00.440
Okay, please get up.

18:06.080 --> 18:08.680
With an "Eagle Spread Its Wings,"

18:08.760 --> 18:10.560
I offed the little monster in a second.

18:10.640 --> 18:13.360
My apprentice knelt down and said,

18:13.440 --> 18:17.240
"Master, please take me
as your apprentice."

18:18.160 --> 18:19.440
I never thought

18:19.520 --> 18:23.880
I could be spreading my influence
so soon in a game.

18:24.400 --> 18:26.960
I feel so good about myself. Yeah?

18:27.040 --> 18:30.400
I only feel a breakdown coming.

18:30.480 --> 18:32.000
Sisi?

18:34.560 --> 18:36.560
I feel so good about myself. Yeah?

18:36.880 --> 18:37.840
Bang!

18:38.680 --> 18:39.600
So cruel.

18:46.640 --> 18:49.680
Are you done swiping your phone?

18:50.200 --> 18:52.840
It's bad for the eyes
to be on the phone while you walk.

18:53.400 --> 18:55.640
Anyway, when will you buy a new phone?

18:58.120 --> 19:01.680
I'll buy it after my summer job.
I don't have enough money now.

19:02.600 --> 19:04.240
What are you doing anyway?

19:05.560 --> 19:07.640
A friend and I made a video.

19:07.720 --> 19:09.760
It's being voted on in the forum.

19:10.240 --> 19:13.200
Look! Our votes are leading everyone else.

19:13.720 --> 19:16.320
We've got the contest in the bag. Here.

19:17.160 --> 19:18.000
Let's go.

19:27.360 --> 19:29.600
Where are you, Weiwei?
I need to talk to you.

19:31.120 --> 19:33.080
I'm doing my daily quests, safeguarding
a shipment of cargo. What is it?

19:33.280 --> 19:36.200
I'll meet you in front of
Hangzhou Safeguard Agency.

19:44.800 --> 19:46.440
What's up, Nini?

19:46.600 --> 19:49.600
I have a question for you, Weiwei.

19:50.920 --> 19:52.200
What is it?

19:52.280 --> 19:55.120
If someone offered a large sum of money,

19:55.200 --> 19:58.120
would you be willing to withdraw
from the video contest?

20:01.320 --> 20:02.560
Zhenshui Wuxiang?

20:04.920 --> 20:06.400
You guessed it, Weiwei.

20:09.640 --> 20:11.680
I didn't need to guess. Isn't it obvious?

20:11.760 --> 20:13.160
If I withdraw,

20:13.240 --> 20:14.080
who will benefit directly?

20:17.960 --> 20:20.880
The winning prize
is a seven-colored outfit.

20:20.960 --> 20:24.480
Xiaoyu Yaoyao
seems to have her eye on it.

20:24.560 --> 20:26.840
Zhenshui Wuxiang went behind her back,

20:26.920 --> 20:28.560
and had me make the offer.

20:28.640 --> 20:30.640
After the face-off last time,

20:30.720 --> 20:32.560
it's awkward for him to approach you.

20:32.840 --> 20:35.160
Weiwei, you're not mad, are you?

20:38.800 --> 20:41.240
I'm not mad. I just think it's funny.

20:42.160 --> 20:46.120
If he plans to spend a couple of thousand
or a few hundred thousand to make me quit,

20:46.400 --> 20:48.680
tell him to give up the idea,
before he embarrasses himself further.

20:48.960 --> 20:51.480
Tens of thousands? Hundreds of thousands?

20:51.560 --> 20:53.600
There's no way
Zhenshui would spend that much money.

20:54.200 --> 20:57.840
He made it sound like a few thousand.
Maybe 10,000 at most.

20:57.920 --> 21:00.960
I didn't know you were that rich, Weiwei!

21:01.040 --> 21:02.520
I had no idea!

21:04.280 --> 21:05.640
I'm low-key.

21:06.680 --> 21:07.880
Forget it, then.

21:08.080 --> 21:10.160
Weiwei, you're not mad, are you?

21:10.680 --> 21:13.320
I didn't want to help him,

21:13.400 --> 21:16.360
but he seems to be
truly in love with Xiaoyu Yaoyao.

21:16.560 --> 21:18.200
I was a bit moved by him.

21:18.520 --> 21:21.040
You know what? They met in person.

21:21.120 --> 21:23.040
They're a couple in real life, too.

21:23.120 --> 21:24.560
They're both in Capital City.

21:24.640 --> 21:25.680
You, too. Right?

21:27.320 --> 21:30.720
Yes, the server is called
Capital City Bests.

21:30.800 --> 21:32.480
A lot of players live here.

21:36.960 --> 21:38.240
Speaking of which,

21:38.480 --> 21:40.080
Naihe and his team

21:40.160 --> 21:42.160
probably go to school here, too?

21:42.920 --> 21:46.480
I'm in Tianjin.
Otherwise, we could meet up and hang out.

21:47.120 --> 21:49.280
By the way, Zhenshui is really handsome.

21:49.640 --> 21:50.720
I have their photo.

21:50.800 --> 21:51.640
Do you want to see, Weiwei?

21:53.520 --> 21:54.800
Not interested.

21:55.720 --> 21:58.120
Hey, Weiwei,
you've met Yixiao Naihe, right?

21:58.200 --> 21:59.600
Is he handsome? Tell me!

22:03.080 --> 22:03.920
No.

22:07.760 --> 22:10.000
Anyway, I should go.

22:10.080 --> 22:12.160
I have a monster-offing date
at five o'clock.

22:16.520 --> 22:19.000
You and your team are all
in Capital City. Right?

22:25.120 --> 22:26.200
I'll go off some monsters.

22:41.560 --> 22:43.400
You're shameless.

22:43.480 --> 22:45.400
You hide behind the missus
and get the reward for free?

22:47.120 --> 22:50.000
You get used to being a deadbeat
after a while.

22:51.240 --> 22:53.440
Guys like you,
who don't have the missus' protection,

22:54.240 --> 22:55.120
will never understand.

22:57.400 --> 22:58.240
Get him!

23:44.960 --> 23:48.240
It's bad enough that you're ungrateful.
You stepped on me, too!

23:48.520 --> 23:49.760
I'm turning in my grave!

23:53.960 --> 23:55.560
A married couple does think alike!

23:58.200 --> 24:00.400
We can't interfere in their domestic life.

24:03.600 --> 24:05.120
I didn't see you guys.

24:05.200 --> 24:06.760
Why were you lying on the ground?

24:07.280 --> 24:08.520
What a phony!

24:08.600 --> 24:10.000
I don't believe you didn't see

24:10.080 --> 24:11.840
how Nai abused us just now.

24:13.280 --> 24:15.600
This is called selective blindness.

24:17.520 --> 24:18.480
I knew it.

24:18.560 --> 24:20.080
Neighborhood committee leader
is a tough gig.

24:23.440 --> 24:25.440
The Video Contest has concluded.

24:27.960 --> 24:29.680
The winner of the Video Contest is...

24:29.760 --> 24:31.720
"Girl Bandit Abducts Groom"

24:31.800 --> 24:33.680
by Yixiao Naihe and Luwei Weiwei!

24:35.240 --> 24:36.480
Naihe, we won!

24:37.600 --> 24:38.440
I see it.

24:43.080 --> 24:45.760
Well deserved. The post-production
seems to be done by Yixiao Naihe.

24:45.840 --> 24:47.760
A master of pen and sword. Unbelievable!

24:50.680 --> 24:52.560
The prize delivery is also unbelievable.

24:53.320 --> 24:55.440
Right? What if Naihe gets knocked over?

25:04.840 --> 25:06.000
Wow!

25:06.080 --> 25:08.320
Mrs. Nai, put it on! Try it!

25:29.440 --> 25:30.280
You should put it on, too!

25:37.920 --> 25:39.960
Try changing colors. It's got seven.

25:43.720 --> 25:45.000
Yes! Try it out.

25:50.240 --> 25:53.600
Six colors? I think it's missing one?

25:54.360 --> 25:56.280
Green.

26:03.400 --> 26:04.480
Green?

26:04.800 --> 26:06.920
Naihe's regular headwear
is a white ribbon,

26:07.240 --> 26:09.880
yet the seven-colored outfit's
headwear is green.

26:10.200 --> 26:12.200
The game designer probably did that
on purpose.

26:12.680 --> 26:14.160
Something's wrong with Nai.

26:14.720 --> 26:17.400
He refuses to wear
the matching outfit with Mrs. Nai.

26:17.760 --> 26:19.360
Could it be...

26:21.400 --> 26:22.960
We're an old couple now.

26:23.200 --> 26:24.360
We don't care about superficial stuff.

26:27.760 --> 26:30.080
Have fun, guys.
I'm going to take a stroll.

26:48.080 --> 26:49.600
We're an old couple now.

26:49.840 --> 26:51.040
We don't care about superficial stuff.

26:53.600 --> 26:55.480
What a gossip killer!

26:55.720 --> 26:58.200
Luwei Weiwei, you're a party pooper.

26:58.280 --> 26:59.680
Like...

27:00.400 --> 27:01.680
You've met Yixiao Naihe, right?

27:01.760 --> 27:03.680
Is he handsome? Tell me!

27:06.520 --> 27:08.920
If Naihe wants to exchange photos,

27:09.480 --> 27:10.800
will I do it?

27:12.480 --> 27:15.000
I think I will.

27:16.240 --> 27:18.160
What if he wants to meet?

27:19.840 --> 27:22.760
I think I will, too.

27:24.240 --> 27:25.800
The way Naihe is,

27:26.080 --> 27:28.000
I don't think he'll ask for photos,

27:28.080 --> 27:29.520
let alone asking to meet.

27:30.520 --> 27:32.880
But if we don't ever meet,

27:33.240 --> 27:35.040
once I quit gaming,

27:35.120 --> 27:36.680
will I part with Naihe forever?

27:40.360 --> 27:44.240
Bok choy, getting yellow in the earth

27:44.640 --> 27:48.800
It's before dawn, and I'm washing socks

27:49.880 --> 27:54.280
The northern wind howls,

27:54.720 --> 27:59.440
I still have a ton of socks

28:01.560 --> 28:02.560
What's up, Girly Mei?

28:02.640 --> 28:04.720
I heard your siren's call from far away.

28:06.560 --> 28:07.480
What's that smell?

28:12.480 --> 28:14.040
Darn it! What's that? Poison gas?

28:15.920 --> 28:17.560
It stings my eyes! I can't open them!

28:17.640 --> 28:18.480
Get lost!

28:19.040 --> 28:20.600
Study acting, if you're so good!

28:21.640 --> 28:22.840
Many girls study acting.

28:23.600 --> 28:24.840
I'm telling you,

28:24.920 --> 28:26.800
if you ever call me by that nickname,

28:26.880 --> 28:28.880
- I'll give you Yu Banshan's socks.
- Don't.

28:28.960 --> 28:30.920
I want to live another day.

28:33.280 --> 28:35.760
Washing socks? What's gotten into you?

28:36.040 --> 28:37.520
You have no idea!

28:37.800 --> 28:42.800
Nai... He's back!

28:42.880 --> 28:49.400
Bok choy, getting yellow in the earth

28:49.600 --> 28:51.920
Old masters...

28:52.000 --> 28:55.440
- Goodness!
- ...Tidying up the room...

28:55.520 --> 28:58.600
Xiao Nai, how did you manage this?

28:59.200 --> 29:00.440
It has nothing to do with me.

29:00.720 --> 29:02.160
They're sanitation freaks.

29:02.240 --> 29:03.760
They thought it's time to clean.

29:04.320 --> 29:05.280
I suddenly feel like,

29:05.360 --> 29:06.840
I should go back and clean, too.

29:06.920 --> 29:07.760
See you.

29:09.680 --> 29:12.000
Girly Mei, lend me your laundry detergent.

29:12.080 --> 29:13.280
I haven't used that stuff in ages.

29:14.600 --> 29:15.960
- See you.
- Do you want rags?

29:16.920 --> 29:17.760
No.

29:22.360 --> 29:23.680
I think our dorm

29:23.760 --> 29:26.880
at least meets the standard
of a five-star hotel.

29:26.960 --> 29:29.000
No more worries about girls coming over.

29:29.560 --> 29:32.320
You'll regret it, Nai.

29:32.400 --> 29:34.000
You had Yu Banshan's socks

29:34.080 --> 29:35.160
to fend off the girls for you.

29:35.240 --> 29:36.080
Now, they're nice and clean,

29:36.160 --> 29:39.800
emitting such pleasant aroma,

29:39.880 --> 29:41.520
girls will no longer be deterred.

29:41.600 --> 29:43.800
They'll be swarming into our dorm.

29:44.280 --> 29:45.120
Dry them.

29:49.400 --> 29:51.720
Yu,

29:51.800 --> 29:53.880
why didn't we learn from our mistake?

29:54.320 --> 29:57.400
Why must we play that game with Nai?

29:59.080 --> 30:00.600
Back in the day,

30:01.120 --> 30:03.160
when we first arrived at Qing University,

30:03.560 --> 30:06.120
too naive in our youth...

30:13.000 --> 30:14.880
How old are you guys?

30:15.320 --> 30:17.040
I started school a year late.

30:17.120 --> 30:18.680
I'm 20, probably the oldest.

30:19.000 --> 30:21.680
- I'm 19.
- Me, too.

30:21.760 --> 30:23.800
You're 19, too? I bet I'm older.

30:23.880 --> 30:24.920
I was born in January.

30:25.000 --> 30:29.120
Fine. I'm a Libra,
half love and half beauty.

30:30.360 --> 30:32.920
Looks like you're the youngest.

30:33.480 --> 30:35.080
I'm the oldest. I'll rank everyone.

30:35.400 --> 30:38.040
I'm Big Bro. You're Second Bro.
You're Third Bro.

30:38.680 --> 30:40.840
That makes you Fourth Bro. Fourth Bro!

30:41.080 --> 30:43.600
That doesn't roll off the tongue.
We'll call you Lil' Bro.

30:45.840 --> 30:47.440
Ranking by age is pointless.

30:47.880 --> 30:51.560
We're men. We should be ranked by ability.

31:10.320 --> 31:12.560
I lost again!

31:13.240 --> 31:16.200
Fine, Lil' Bro. You can be Big Bro.

31:16.720 --> 31:19.280
That's okay. I'll settle for Third Bro.

31:19.800 --> 31:20.640
You'd do that?

31:21.160 --> 31:23.880
Big Bro is the acknowledged
dorm supervisor, in charge of maintenance.

31:29.080 --> 31:30.200
We're still too naive!

31:30.280 --> 31:32.280
Why did we have to spar with him?

31:32.360 --> 31:35.720
He uses reverse psychology every time!
Impulse is the original sin!

31:35.800 --> 31:36.840
Original sin!

31:39.720 --> 31:41.680
Wait, I have a call.

31:43.720 --> 31:44.880
Unknown number?

31:46.440 --> 31:47.600
Hello?

31:48.000 --> 31:51.360
Hello, is this Mr. Yu Banshan?

31:53.360 --> 31:54.680
Who's calling, please?

31:55.760 --> 31:58.120
Is it a good time to talk?

31:59.200 --> 32:00.240
It's a girl!

32:00.960 --> 32:02.840
Hurry.

32:06.320 --> 32:09.720
Hi, Miss. Yes, I can talk...

32:10.880 --> 32:12.560
Who's this?

32:13.280 --> 32:14.400
Here's the thing,

32:14.480 --> 32:16.160
I'm calling from Zhenyi Tech's
game development division.

32:16.240 --> 32:17.960
I'm Xiaoli, Mr. Li's secretary.

32:18.280 --> 32:20.840
You visited our office, remember?

32:22.520 --> 32:23.920
Yes, I do.

32:24.560 --> 32:25.760
Since the meeting,

32:25.840 --> 32:27.920
Mr. Li has been talking about you nonstop.

32:28.160 --> 32:29.400
He's very taken with you.

32:29.480 --> 32:31.640
Are you available to meet soon?

32:31.720 --> 32:34.440
Mr. Li wants to invite you to a meal,
just you.

32:36.320 --> 32:37.160
Just me?

32:41.120 --> 32:42.960
I'll call you back.

32:43.040 --> 32:44.480
Okay? I'm a little busy now.

32:45.320 --> 32:46.160
Bye.

32:51.360 --> 32:53.440
- Who was it?
- Houzi, charge my phone.

32:56.800 --> 32:58.880
Nai, remember Mr. Li from Zhenyi?

33:00.680 --> 33:01.520
He wants to meet with you?

33:02.200 --> 33:05.080
Wow. Are you a sorcerer or what?

33:05.440 --> 33:08.200
- He only invited you?
- That's right.

33:08.720 --> 33:10.240
His secretary called me.

33:10.480 --> 33:13.720
She emphasized "just me,"
and asked me to keep it from you.

33:14.600 --> 33:19.280
Her tone of voice was so seductive.

33:19.640 --> 33:21.440
She blew smoke up my butt, too!
What gives?

33:22.640 --> 33:23.480
Yu,

33:24.280 --> 33:27.400
they're trying to lure you in
with a beauty.

33:27.800 --> 33:28.640
Get lost!

33:29.240 --> 33:31.080
Am I the kind to succumb to beauty?

33:31.800 --> 33:33.880
- They should at least send a few!
- Animal!

33:33.960 --> 33:38.080
Enough. What are they really after?

33:39.200 --> 33:40.360
Are they trying to poach you?

33:42.400 --> 33:44.160
They've done that before.

33:44.760 --> 33:46.920
The year before last,
they launched a mobile card game.

33:47.120 --> 33:47.960
Remember?

33:48.960 --> 33:49.960
Yes.

33:50.040 --> 33:51.920
Over 100 million in monthly revenue;
a legend in the industry.

33:52.560 --> 33:53.400
That's right.

33:55.880 --> 33:58.160
The game was developed by a little studio.

33:58.240 --> 33:59.880
Zhenyi Tech failed to acquire them.

33:59.960 --> 34:01.880
So they poached the entire team
with lucrative pay.

34:02.360 --> 34:04.680
They made a similar mobile game
and launched it first.

34:04.880 --> 34:06.560
They might want to do the same this time.

34:07.840 --> 34:10.120
The entire team got poached?

34:10.199 --> 34:11.719
Isn't that certain death for the studio?

34:12.080 --> 34:14.520
Darn it! That's so ruthless!

34:17.199 --> 34:18.280
Nai,

34:18.400 --> 34:20.800
if I get seduced, you have to protect me.

34:21.679 --> 34:23.800
If you're scared, then don't go.

34:23.880 --> 34:24.760
I'm telling you guys,

34:25.159 --> 34:27.719
bros before girls.

34:28.159 --> 34:29.719
No one should succumb

34:29.800 --> 34:30.920
to the temptation of money,

34:31.000 --> 34:33.480
women, house, or cars. Okay?

34:33.840 --> 34:35.960
If push comes to shove...

34:36.760 --> 34:38.880
- I'll go!
- I'll go!

34:38.960 --> 34:39.800
Go to hell!

34:40.560 --> 34:42.000
Me! I'll go!

34:42.080 --> 34:43.880
I'm an expert programmer.

34:44.159 --> 34:46.600
Banshan, if you recommend me to go,

34:46.679 --> 34:48.600
I'll give you 30 percent.

34:50.239 --> 34:51.360
By the way, Banshan,

34:52.040 --> 34:53.199
did you give them your number?

34:53.920 --> 34:54.920
No.

34:55.560 --> 34:56.560
That's right!

34:56.760 --> 34:57.680
I never provided my number.

34:57.760 --> 34:58.880
Why do they have it?

34:59.160 --> 35:02.200
They went the whole nine yards
to get your number.

35:02.520 --> 35:04.200
This is no small deal.

35:04.600 --> 35:05.640
They're well prepared.

35:07.200 --> 35:09.560
Nai, I didn't give them an answer
on the phone.

35:10.640 --> 35:13.680
They want to poach me?
I'll reject them outright.

35:14.280 --> 35:15.680
Why reject them?

35:16.080 --> 35:17.520
Isn't this a good opportunity?

35:19.320 --> 35:21.400
What? Why is it a good opportunity?

35:21.760 --> 35:24.280
When Nai smiles mysteriously like that,

35:24.360 --> 35:26.160
somebody will get burnt.

35:26.240 --> 35:27.680
So chilling! So scary!

35:28.760 --> 35:30.120
I'm scared, too!

35:30.240 --> 35:31.320
How do you want to do this?

35:32.840 --> 35:33.760
Let's go eat first.

35:34.520 --> 35:35.760
You're too much!

35:35.840 --> 35:38.040
Wait, my phone's only been charging
for two minutes.

35:38.120 --> 35:41.240
Your phone can last two hours,
after five minutes of charging.

35:41.320 --> 35:42.520
It'll be fine. Let's go eat.

35:42.600 --> 35:44.480
Wait for me. I need to change.

35:45.120 --> 35:46.360
We're only getting food.

35:46.440 --> 35:48.680
- What do you need to change?
- What do you know?

35:48.760 --> 35:50.640
Wherever Nai is, there'll be girls.

35:50.720 --> 35:51.960
I want the girls to see

35:52.040 --> 35:53.800
my best side.

35:54.000 --> 35:55.240
- I'll change, too.
- Me, too.

35:55.320 --> 35:56.160
Hurry. Let's go!

36:26.400 --> 36:28.560
It feels so great to have Nai back.

36:28.640 --> 36:29.680
Center of attention.

36:29.840 --> 36:30.800
In that moment,

36:30.880 --> 36:32.840
I thought I was extra handsome.

36:34.280 --> 36:35.720
Gotta be handsome.

36:40.440 --> 36:42.520
- So hot!
- He's so cute!

36:49.880 --> 36:51.480
Let's go to him!

36:53.400 --> 36:54.600
Where's Nai?

36:54.720 --> 36:57.160
He left us to get in line?

37:07.440 --> 37:09.120
Xiao Nai?

37:09.200 --> 37:11.480
Xiao Nai has come to the cafeteria!

37:12.080 --> 37:12.920
I see him.

37:17.960 --> 37:20.960
I'm able to stand in the same line
as Xiao Nai!

37:21.040 --> 37:23.120
I'm so lucky!

37:23.720 --> 37:25.000
It's the next line over.

37:26.320 --> 37:28.400
- I've decided!
- What?

37:29.480 --> 37:30.400
Whatever he orders,

37:30.480 --> 37:32.640
we'll have that for lunch.

37:32.840 --> 37:34.960
Excellent decision!

37:49.240 --> 37:51.720
But your decision is hard to realize.

37:51.960 --> 37:54.760
Xiao Nai is behind us.
We'll get up before him.

37:54.960 --> 37:56.320
We should instead pray for

37:56.400 --> 37:58.320
sitting at the same table with him.

37:59.400 --> 38:01.160
Don't even think about that.

38:01.600 --> 38:04.240
It's too much of a drain on luck.

38:04.480 --> 38:07.600
I worry we might use up all of it.

38:17.160 --> 38:18.120
Next!

38:20.160 --> 38:22.000
- What would you like?
- These three.

38:28.680 --> 38:30.280
- His line is moving so fast.
- That one.

38:30.360 --> 38:32.320
- Your wish is about to come true.
- And this.

38:32.640 --> 38:34.200
The lunch lady is moving so slow,
I want to cry.

38:34.280 --> 38:36.400
I'm so touched.

38:39.080 --> 38:39.920
What would you like?

38:40.360 --> 38:41.480
- Sweet-and-sour pork.
- Sweet-and-sour pork.

38:51.080 --> 38:52.560
There's only one portion left.

38:52.920 --> 38:53.760
So...

38:54.320 --> 38:56.360
It's fine. I'll have Salted Chicken.

38:57.560 --> 39:00.120
I don't want it, either. This is fine.

39:01.920 --> 39:03.480
I want the sweet-and-sour pork.
I'll take it all.

39:20.760 --> 39:21.720
Thanks, bro!

39:32.280 --> 39:33.760
Here. I got some more.

39:37.400 --> 39:38.680
Bros,

39:38.840 --> 39:41.720
how come it's a guy
at the lunch counter today?

39:42.600 --> 39:43.760
He's very nice, though.

39:43.840 --> 39:46.280
Look! My portion is extra big.

39:46.480 --> 39:47.720
My sautéed mixed greens

39:47.880 --> 39:50.840
have extra strips of meat.

39:53.880 --> 39:55.120
I thought it was odd.

39:55.440 --> 39:56.880
How come mine has no meat?

39:56.960 --> 39:57.920
Not even a speck.

39:58.560 --> 40:00.320
Mine has no meat, either.

40:02.080 --> 40:04.840
What do you know? This is called luck.

40:04.920 --> 40:06.600
You're no match for me.

40:08.720 --> 40:10.960
He gave you more meat,

40:11.320 --> 40:13.560
because he saw your baby face
and under-developed body.

40:14.320 --> 40:15.920
Who are you calling under-developed?

40:16.000 --> 40:17.440
We can go back and compare!

40:17.520 --> 40:18.640
Enough!

40:18.920 --> 40:19.760
Your conversation

40:19.840 --> 40:21.560
is so innocent that I could barf.

40:22.760 --> 40:25.560
Anyway, we've never been
to this cafeteria.

40:26.080 --> 40:27.440
It's far from our dorm.

40:27.840 --> 40:29.720
What's going on, Nai?

40:29.800 --> 40:30.640
Why are we eating here today?

40:31.360 --> 40:32.360
It's a random pick.

40:34.040 --> 40:35.480
I think this cafeteria is nice.

40:35.840 --> 40:37.960
I'm in love with this cafeteria.

40:38.040 --> 40:40.120
Let's eat here from now on.

40:46.000 --> 40:47.640
Why didn't you listen to me?

40:47.720 --> 40:49.520
We should sit closer to Xiao Nai.

40:49.600 --> 40:51.840
We didn't get to eat the same food.

40:51.920 --> 40:55.120
My only consolation is that
I have the same drink as him.

40:57.920 --> 40:59.920
Why do I feel a little guilty?

41:01.160 --> 41:02.440
Guilty over what?

41:04.320 --> 41:05.520
Why do I feel like,

41:05.600 --> 41:07.040
ever since I lied to Cao Guang

41:07.120 --> 41:09.360
that I want a boyfriend like Xiao Nai,

41:09.560 --> 41:11.880
I've been running into him more often?

41:12.520 --> 41:13.880
One really shouldn't do bad things.

41:14.400 --> 41:15.520
I feel so guilty.

41:15.600 --> 41:17.280
Tell me! Why do you feel guilty?

41:18.240 --> 41:19.080
Just eat.

41:20.720 --> 41:21.840
I have to go study later.

41:22.440 --> 41:25.200
In-Game Couples Battle Championship
registration opens tonight.

41:25.280 --> 41:27.000
I have to hurry back. Eat up!

41:30.960 --> 41:32.840
I need to use the toilet. You guys go on.

41:38.000 --> 41:39.000
Eat!

41:41.080 --> 41:42.000
Quit staring.

41:44.160 --> 41:45.680
It starts next Friday night,

41:45.760 --> 41:46.920
for a month.

41:47.400 --> 41:50.240
If we can get into the finals,

41:50.320 --> 41:51.360
after the competition,

41:51.440 --> 41:53.880
I still have a week to study English.

41:56.960 --> 41:57.800
My schedule is fine.

41:58.680 --> 42:00.120
What about you?

42:02.880 --> 42:03.720
It's fine.

42:04.120 --> 42:06.920
If there's a match,
remind me the day before.

42:10.040 --> 42:12.800
Sure. I'll be your calendar.

42:18.800 --> 42:21.920
Nai, In-Game Couples Battle Championship
is about to begin.

42:22.080 --> 42:23.840
It's an all-servers competition,
full of master-level players.

42:23.920 --> 42:26.000
You should train with us first.

42:26.080 --> 42:28.600
Yeah, pretend we're your opponents.

42:28.680 --> 42:30.960
Let's do a mock match.

42:31.040 --> 42:32.640
Our opponents are in-game couples.

42:33.120 --> 42:34.720
Which one of you is the guy? And the girl?

42:35.480 --> 42:37.160
- I'm the guy, of course!
- I'm the guy, of course!

42:37.560 --> 42:39.800
- I'm heavier.
- I'm taller.

42:39.880 --> 42:41.800
- I'm cuter.
- I'm prettier.

42:41.880 --> 42:43.360
Must you make me crush you?

42:43.440 --> 42:45.280
- In your dreams!
- Bring it on!

45:12.120 --> 45:14.560
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
